{"id":48383,"title":"[High-tech medical care in surgical endocrinology].","abstract":"The number of patients with endocrine system diseases increases annually. Widespread introduction of screening programs and improvement of laboratory and instrumental diagnostic is one of the most important causes for this. Treatment of patients with endocrine system diseases within the high-tech medical care leads to perform the unique surgical interventions. It increases survival and patients' life quality. ","date":"2014-08-22","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25146543","annotations":[{"name":"Endocrine system","weight":0.878636,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endocrine_system"},{"name":"Endocrinology","weight":0.820237,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endocrinology"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.793722,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Quality of life","weight":0.767518,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_of_life"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.754651,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.701843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.604887,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Screening (medicine)","weight":0.599803,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Screening_(medicine)"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.528221,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Laboratory","weight":0.478734,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laboratory"},{"name":"Endocrine disease","weight":0.225141,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endocrine_disease"},{"name":"Instrumental","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Instrumental"},{"name":"High tech","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.